Package com.i2group.apollo.auditservice.transport

Contains classes for the service that retrieves audit entries about items in the Analysis Repository.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuditEntry
    A piece of audit information that references the affected Item and the Principal who triggered the change.
    AuditResults
    Contains the AuditEntrys that form the results of a request to the audit service, and an indication of whether the permitted number of results was exceeded.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuditEntryType
    Indicates the type of an AuditEntry.

Package com.i2group.apollo.auditservice.transport Description
